   <name>
    <narrative xml:lang="EN">CAME operates paper mills in Cali (Colombia) and Chincha (Peru).  In addition, it operates corrugating and box making operations in Cali and  Mosquera (Colombia), Lurin (Peru), as well as near Valencia (Venezuela), and Quito (Ecuador).  The two plants in Cali are separate sites within the urban area of the city.  The other sites are all located in industrial parks situated on the edge of cities.  Some portion of the capital investment comprising the project is allocated for each of these sites.  The most significant investment, a cogeneration plant, would be installed at the paper mill site in Cali.</narrative>
